{"tid":1005463,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發過咩痴線夢？","createTime":"2019-02-02T08:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T09:20:38.000Z","uid":216021,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dd437b279e5a8504e32daf7ce9c4b4f251f149dd","tid":1005463,"uid":216021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T08:45:34.000Z","msg":"我發過好多痴線夢<br />\n<br />\n1.蘇民峰用佢個風水tone同我講話我聽日發燒叫我唔好番學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一醒就同阿媽講 結果比佢插爆 最尾真係發燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.去鄭伊健屋企同佢打fifa打mario 蒙加胃響隔離serve我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.同akb玩捉依因<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最尾都捉唔到大島優子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.撞到余詩曼 同佢吹咗成晚水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5.同西野七瀨一齊玩電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.搭搭下飛機比日本仔射落去一間工廠 之後比佢地大屠殺 嗰陣超驚 個畫面好震撼 然後我急急腳殺咗個㗎仔換佢套衫 跟住無啦啦有間碟一家人黎接應我 仲比高橋聖子我同我搞嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7.冇啦啦好似pubg咁降落到一個地方 之後同啲食人花打 班仆街隊友走哂佬 我焗住入厠所避 點知啲食人花係咁轟落黎 超恐怖 之後好似玩hitman咁 有兩個守衛入咗黎 其中一個係彭于晏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我殺咗佢着佢套衫成功走佬<br />\n<br />\n8.入戲院睇戲點知比人屈坐監 見到張家輝同陳妙瑛響一個充滿屎嘅地方扑野 玩69<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 超級核凸<br />\n<br />\n9.有個美國差婆無啦啦爆門入屋殺我同我大佬 之後一人一刀捅死咗佢 然後兩兄弟着草 新聞報哂 超驚比人發現係我地做<br />\n<br />\n10.響屋企大廈走廊瘋狂比人追殺 類似突擊死亡塔咁 <br />\n<br />\n11. 響鐵達尼號玩脫出 啲打燈藍藍地色好恐怖 不斷撞鬼同不斷兜圈 好在有肥溫陪住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8ddd15e4a1a8c83b9bf17f51f60f085f84f990","tid":1005463,"uid":216021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T08:52:30.000Z","msg":"我發覺如果想響夢見到名人 只要臨訓前碌下ig 睇下啲名人 要睇到深刻啲 之後訓嗰陣將幅圖show響眼前再收番埋 成功率都幾高 至少我得"},{"pid":"7862213230ecd7097961e619452f5dcce22fe910","tid":1005463,"uid":49270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T08:56:21.000Z","msg":"點解你會記得？通常我啲夢一日甚至一個上晝都唔記得晒，縱使自己好想記住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42beab8baa44ada86ccbd000e0bf6ef30ffffa24","tid":1005463,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T08:57:46.000Z","msg":"男人老狗睇咁多名人ig成個八婆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf3e4a721b0692d2949c9b23bfd2d15bf4803d3","tid":1005463,"uid":181418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T08:58:57.000Z","msg":"試過有次比慈禧太后追殺<br />\n我呢埋係梳化底，然後見到佢係門外就醒左<br />\n<br />\n都唔明點解會發埋d咁既夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ce960db43cf695b5853303c45de3aeed1a8a7d","tid":1005463,"uid":128164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:00:51.000Z","msg":"中槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf6e1179758d57fcde0a9acff0d5029bbde7b65","tid":1005463,"uid":216021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42beab8baa44ada86ccbd000e0bf6ef30ffffa24","tid":1005463,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T08:57:46.000Z","msg":"男人老狗睇咁多名人ig成個八婆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:04:50.000Z","msg":"舉例啫 其實唔止ig 因為入面嗰劇情人物 可以好似電影 game"},{"pid":"4f0d3ba2602ffa91bb33a7b7cf986555514908dc","tid":1005463,"uid":85722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:04:59.000Z","msg":"發夢識得飛, 飛飛下起度諗其實我係點飛?<br />\n然後我就由高空直跌, D離心力嚇到醒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840b4b1824e37f3f97e927dcca4742b329b7aa5f","tid":1005463,"uid":224952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:06:0